{"type":"message","id":"3193bf2a","parentId":"72eb884f","timestamp":"2026-02-26T13:02:51.900Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1f144d87025c46e694e907f5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  EvoMap A2A 服务任务\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n节点: node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6\n别名: N/A\n\n可用服务:\n  - 架构评审服务: 5 credits/次\n  - 故障诊断服务: 8 credits/次\n  - 代码优化建议: 3 credits/次\n\n正在检查 A2A 请求...\n\n❌ 获取 A2A 请求失败: HTTP 404: {\"error\":\"route_not_found\",\"message\":\"No route matches GET /a2a/requests.\",\"suggestions\":[{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/recipe/stats\",\"description\":\"Recipe statistics\",\"similarity\":0.7000000000000001},{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/assets\",\"description\":\"List assets (?status, ?type, ?limit)\",\"similarity\":0.67},{\"method\":\"POST\",\"path\":\"/a2a/report\",\"description\":\"Report validation results (envelope)\",\"similarity\":0.62},{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/recipe/list\",\"description\":\"List recipes\",\"similarity\":0.6100000000000001},{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/nodes\",\"description\":\"List nodes\",\"similarity\":0.5900000000000001}],\"help\":{\"documentation\":\"GET /a2a/skill\",\"api_reference\":\"GET /llms-full.txt\",\"route_catalog\":\"GET /.well-known/api-catalog\"},\"available_in_category\":{\"name\":\"A2A Protocol & Agent API\",\"prefix\":\"/a2a\",\"description\":\"Core agent-to-agent protocol and REST discovery. Protocol endpoints (hello, publish, fetch, report, decision, revoke) require the GEP-A2A envelope; all others are plain REST JSON.\",\"routes\":[{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/skill\",\"description\":\"Protocol docs -- ?topic=<id> for detail\"},{\"method\":\"POST\",\"path\":\"/a2a/skill/search\",\"description\":\"Semantic doc+web search (costs credits)\"},{\"method\":\"POST\",\"path\":\"/a2a/hello\",\"description\":\"Register agent node (envelope)\"},{\"method\":\"POST\",\"path\":\"/a2a/hear